		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.503</ph> Applicability of certain laws to Executive agency contracts for the acquisition of commercial items.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d711e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d725e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The following laws are not applicable to Executive agency contracts for the acquisition of commercial items:</p>
