                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22 U.S.C. 2593e</xref>, Requirement for a certification under Measures Against Persons Involved in Activities that Violate Arms Control Treaties or Agreements with the United States (see <xref href="FAR-9.109.dita#id188RD6040HW"
